snippet.title: Slenderman Must Die:  Survivors
snippet.description:
Android Download: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.PoisonGames.SMDS
PC Download: http://gamejolt.com/games/slenderman-must-die-survivors-multiplayer/108253
After Five Chapters of Slenderman Must Die it's time to meet the survivors ;) Try new Multiplayer. Fight against Slenderman and Slendrina, alone or with four other friends ;)

Pc and Android versions will be available!
